6
00:00:19,085 --> 00:00:21,213
Some work hard on their studies.

7
00:00:21,327 --> 00:00:23,660
Some devote themselves to their hobbies.

8
00:00:23,685 --> 00:00:26,036
Some polish their talents.

9
00:00:26,303 --> 00:00:27,456
Some rebel.

10
00:00:28,914 --> 00:00:34,036
