the amalgamation that is adolescence.

12
00:00:40,166 --> 00:00:42,921
And, what was Mob doing during this precious time?

13
00:00:43,114 --> 00:00:46,515
Working as an assistant for a psychic at 300 yen an hour.

14
00:00:47,282 --> 00:00:50,591
