It actually feels pretty good!

31
00:03:11,456 --> 00:03:14,429
Sorcery Crush!

32
00:03:14,456 --> 00:03:16,046
Finishing blow!

33
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:18,738
This is one of Reigen's special moves.

34
00:03:18,956 --> 00:03:21,642
He relieves the stress from physical fatigue,

35
00:03:21,748 --> 00:03:24,486
and gets rid of stiff shoulders and back pain.

36
00:03:28,089 --> 00:03:30,342
I believe that I was able to lift the curse.

37
00:03:30,549 --> 00:03:31,998
Do your shoulders still feel heavy?

38
00:03:32,023 --> 00:03:34,099
No! I'm sorry that I doubted you.

39
00:03:34,179 --> 00:03:35,822
Everything feels so much better!

40
00:03:35,847 --> 00:03:37,645
May I come again for a follow-up?

41
00:03:37,934 --> 00:03:39,258
That'd be no problem!

42
00:03:39,998 --> 00:03:40,891
