The fee for a 40-minute massage is 3,800 yen.

44
00:03:44,627 --> 00:03:46,622
Idiot! Don't call it a massage fee!

45
00:03:46,647 --> 00:03:48,273
Call it the "curse-dispelling" fee!

46
00:03:48,546 --> 00:03:50,498
Two hundred yen is your change.

47
00:03:50,873 --> 00:03:52,011
Hey, here you go, Mob.

48
00:03:52,071 --> 00:03:52,998
