better at these massages, lately.

51
00:04:00,477 --> 00:04:01,331
Well, yeah.

52
00:04:01,486 --> 00:04:04,973
I've been tryin' different things to
improve, like reading up on some new techniques.

53
00:04:05,121 --> 00:04:07,997
'Course, it's only effective 'cause of my spiritual power.

54
00:04:10,323 --> 00:04:11,332
Hot!

55
00:04:11,814 --> 00:04:13,039
Such a waste!

56
00:04:15,134 --> 00:04:16,717
Master, I...

57
00:04:16,820 --> 00:04:18,646
I've been thinking about something...

58
00:04:19,006 --> 00:04:20,700
Well, this is a rare occasion.

59
00:04:20,998 --> 00:04:22,664
You don't start conversations.

60
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:23,248
Well...

61
00:04:23,273 --> 00:04:26,615
I can use a little ESP, and
I'm different from other people,

62
00:04:26,801 --> 00:04:28,812
so I came to discuss that with you

63
00:04:28,838 --> 00:04:30,825
and then I ended up becoming your student.

64
00:04:31,184 --> 00:04:35,863
At the time, I didn't have anybody else
to talk to, so I was and am grateful...

65
00:04:36,377 --> 00:04:39,473
