79
00:05:14,638 --> 00:05:16,687
Be in a band? Dance?

80
00:05:16,748 --> 00:05:18,393
Hitchhike across the country?

81
00:05:18,527 --> 00:05:21,110
No, I don't have anything particular in mind.

82
00:05:21,884 --> 00:05:23,203
Okay. Listen, Mob.

83
00:05:23,248 --> 00:05:26,673
I understand what you're going through,
but there's no need to rush into things.

84
00:05:26,733 --> 00:05:29,794
