98
00:06:06,248 --> 00:06:08,487
Maybe Takenaka changed his mind and came back.

99
00:06:08,512 --> 00:06:10,892
That's gotta be it! Takenaka!

100
00:06:12,414 --> 00:06:15,700
I just received a submission
of resignation from this club.

101
00:06:15,873 --> 00:06:16,664
It's...

102
00:06:16,701 --> 00:06:18,260
The student council!

103
00:06:18,737 --> 00:06:20,514
This club... is abolished.

104
00:06:20,539 --> 00:06:21,514
