105
00:06:21,743 --> 00:06:22,903
Wow! Already?!

106
00:06:23,003 --> 00:06:26,159
Sadly, I'm going to have to ask you to gather your things.

107
00:06:26,305 --> 00:06:30,404
I recently had a brand-new club
request for a room just like this.

108
00:06:30,429 --> 00:06:31,056
Hold on!

109
00:06:31,081 --> 00:06:33,179
We've only been down to four members for a few minutes!

110
00:06:33,204 --> 00:06:35,704
I'm not gonna let you get rid of the Telepathy Club!

111
00:06:35,729 --> 00:06:37,973
The bond we share in this Club's too strong!

112
00:06:37,998 --> 00:06:39,889
The student council's got nothing on us!

113
00:06:39,914 --> 00:06:42,900
You think you're all high and mighty
because of how you part your hair?!

114
00:06:42,925 --> 00:06:44,094
Shut your mouths.

115
00:06:44,119 --> 00:06:46,577
You pissants don't really wanna anger me, do you?

116
00:06:47,989 --> 00:06:50,973
If you're that desperate to
keep this joke of a club going...

117
00:06:51,085 --> 00:06:54,752
