121
00:07:03,327 --> 00:07:04,532
Quit your whining!

122
00:07:04,557 --> 00:07:08,081
If we ask everyone we see to join,
we'll be able to snag at least one!

123
00:07:08,166 --> 00:07:09,577
But, that's not gonna happen, now.

124
00:07:09,602 --> 00:07:11,738
The recruiting season ended a long time ago.

125
00:07:11,763 --> 00:07:13,871
No! I'm gonna let this go!

126
00:07:13,896 --> 00:07:18,625
We haven't overcome obstacle after obstacle to
be shot down in such a ridiculous way, have we?!

127
00:07:19,222 --> 00:07:20,516
Uh, president?

128
00:07:21,357 --> 00:07:23,744
We haven't done a single thing.

129
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:31,712
I didn't even know this school had a Telepathy Club.

130
00:07:31,737 --> 00:07:33,307
It's creepy, so forget it.

131
00:07:33,332 --> 00:07:34,580
Nah, I've got a job, guys.

132
00:07:34,605 --> 00:07:36,887
What's the big deal? If it's abolished, it's abolished.

133
00:07:36,912 --> 00:07:39,332
You should be studying. Entrance exams are this year.

134
00:07:39,357 --> 00:07:41,310
