Nope.

142
00:07:54,748 --> 00:07:55,299
Forget it.

143
00:07:55,324 --> 00:07:55,914
Uh, no.

144
00:07:55,986 --> 00:07:57,366
Sounds lame. No.

145
00:08:00,845 --> 00:08:04,679
Guess it really is impossible to
find new members this time of year.

146
00:08:04,879 --> 00:08:07,469
Not to mention we keep getting called "creepy."

147
00:08:07,690 --> 00:08:09,594
Now even I wanna quit.

148
00:08:14,081 --> 00:08:15,539
