149
00:08:15,564 --> 00:08:17,303
You need to calm down, okay?!

150
00:08:17,523 --> 00:08:20,574
The Going-Home Club...

151
00:08:22,081 --> 00:08:22,795
President!

152
00:08:23,109 --> 00:08:23,875
