153
00:08:23,929 --> 00:08:27,192
He's not in any clubs or committees, and
he doesn't have any friends or girlfriends.

154
00:08:27,232 --> 00:08:30,664
Salt's go-homer and all-round bum,
Shigeo Kageyama of Year 2, Class 1.

155
00:08:30,704 --> 00:08:32,712
Well, I'd say he's basically right.

156
00:08:32,831 --> 00:08:34,385
Well done, Inukawa!

157
00:08:34,410 --> 00:08:36,943
Please allow me introduce you to the other members:

158
00:08:36,968 --> 00:08:38,883
Kijibayashi, and Saruta.

159
00:08:38,908 --> 00:08:39,868
Nice to meet you.

160
00:08:39,908 --> 00:08:40,708
How's it goin'?

161
00:08:40,931 --> 00:08:42,904
And I'm the president of this group,

162
00:08:42,929 --> 00:08:44,890
Tome Kurata, Year 3, Class 5.

163
00:08:44,930 --> 00:08:46,865
You can call me All-The-Way Tome.

164
00:08:50,197 --> 00:08:51,963
She's pulling out all the stops!

165
00:08:52,330 --> 00:08:54,857
Tome, huh? Hey, what a coincidence!

166
00:08:54,882 --> 00:08:56,223
That's my grandmother's name.

167
00:08:56,372 --> 00:08:58,875
Uh... See? The fates have brought us together!

168
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,056
There you have it!

169
00:09:00,154 --> 00:09:01,964
Please join the Telepathy Club!

170
00:09:02,057 --> 00:09:02,905
