175
00:09:13,694 --> 00:09:14,789
Ah! President!

176
00:09:14,814 --> 00:09:16,050
I just remembered something!

177
00:09:16,075 --> 00:09:18,290
This guy was sort of famous back in grade school!

178
00:09:18,470 --> 00:09:20,549
He could bend spoons and make erasers move.

179
00:09:20,682 --> 00:09:22,056
You know, like telekinesis!

180
00:09:22,265 --> 00:09:24,322
