187
00:09:40,853 --> 00:09:42,828
Just join and leave, what's the big deal.

188
00:09:42,873 --> 00:09:47,848
No, I have to wait until the student council
meeting is over, then go submit my club admission form.

189
00:09:47,873 --> 00:09:48,522
Wait.

190
00:09:48,547 --> 00:09:50,525
So if I told you to come to work immediately,

191
00:09:50,550 --> 00:09:51,955
