promise I made to the others first?

194
00:09:56,552 --> 00:09:58,447
Then, it's not like you actually want to join?

195
00:09:58,539 --> 00:09:59,847
Not really, no.

196
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,641
'Kay, hurry on over.

197
00:10:01,747 --> 00:10:04,441
Time for you to show 'em how things
are done in the Going-Home Club.

198
00:10:04,761 --> 00:10:07,677
