204
00:10:20,834 --> 00:10:22,527
We're not some stupid sports club!

205
00:10:22,754 --> 00:10:24,208
We're the Telepathy Club!

206
00:10:24,233 --> 00:10:25,466
Huh? You're kidding me.

207
00:10:25,533 --> 00:10:28,335
It's a club where we train to feel telepathic powers.

208
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,181
Uh, that sounds shady as hell.

209
00:10:30,212 --> 00:10:31,357
"Telepathic," huh?

210
00:10:31,382 --> 00:10:32,534
