211
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:34,382
You know exactly what I'm talking about!

212
00:10:34,407 --> 00:10:38,226
I've heard from a reliable source
that Kageyama has telekinesis and ESP!

213
00:10:38,251 --> 00:10:41,639
I bet you're just using him to solve cases
and get more customers 'cause you can't do it

214
00:10:41,664 --> 00:10:43,380
on your own 'cause you're a big phony!

215
00:10:43,516 --> 00:10:44,984
Shut your mouth, amateur!

216
00:10:45,009 --> 00:10:47,330
Don't you dare waste my student's precious time

217
00:10:47,363 --> 00:10:48,889
with your middle-school nonsense!

218
00:10:48,914 --> 00:10:49,517
What?!

219
00:10:50,121 --> 00:10:52,958
Are you saying that you don't
care if they shut down our club?

220
00:10:53,018 --> 00:10:55,742
We'll get kicked out of the room and have nowhere to go!

221
00:10:56,954 --> 00:11:01,331
