judging from what their club sounds like to me.

229
00:11:20,394 --> 00:11:21,574
See through it, Mob!

230
00:11:22,227 --> 00:11:23,804
If that shady club goes down,

231
00:11:23,891 --> 00:11:26,479
it's because it was damn well meant to go down.

232
00:11:26,706 --> 00:11:29,121
If you understand, hurry up and come to work!

233
00:11:29,447 --> 00:11:31,540
