235
00:11:33,872 --> 00:11:36,014
Sorry about that. I'll catch you guys later.

236
00:11:36,087 --> 00:11:37,540
Uh... Wait a sec!

237
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,395
Please, just hear me out, okay?!

238
00:11:39,862 --> 00:11:43,521
Now listen, the president seriously
believes in telepathy and all that stuff,

239
00:11:43,626 --> 00:11:46,829
but honestly, the rest of us here
just wanna lie around and goof off.

240
00:11:47,182 --> 00:11:48,826
