251
00:12:19,045 --> 00:12:21,458
You need to turn down things you don't wanna do.

252
00:12:21,973 --> 00:12:24,360
Right now, the thing I least wanna do...

253
00:12:24,593 --> 00:12:26,839
..is to be dressed up like this.

254
00:12:27,432 --> 00:12:28,799
Oh, there it is.

255
00:12:28,852 --> 00:12:30,657
Saint Highso Girls' Academy.

256
00:12:30,682 --> 00:12:32,797
It's a private all-girls high school.

257
00:12:32,997 --> 00:12:35,965
And, the clients have asked us
both to meet up with them on the roof.

258
00:12:36,092 --> 00:12:36,718
Right.

259
00:12:37,212 --> 00:12:39,195
Stop! What in the world do you think you're doing?

260
00:12:39,220 --> 00:12:39,968
Excuse me?

261
00:12:39,993 --> 00:12:42,030
You heard what I said! Don't play dumb!

262
00:12:42,055 --> 00:12:44,098
Oh, I'm just a student here on my way to class.

263
00:12:44,123 --> 00:12:45,739
Reporting from the front gate.

264
00:12:45,764 --> 00:12:48,257
Suspicious individual here! Requesting backup!

265
00:12:48,417 --> 00:12:50,255
That's kinda mean, isn't it?

266
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:51,958
Can it, you perverted weirdo!

267
00:12:52,198 --> 00:12:53,573
I knew this wouldn't work.

268
00:12:53,732 --> 00:12:55,897
But I'm glad they saw through our disguises.

269
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:58,816
I didn't wanna sneak into the school dressed like this.

270
00:12:59,347 --> 00:13:01,014
That was a close one, huh?

271
00:13:01,180 --> 00:13:03,377
Now hurry along and stay away from that freak.

272
00:13:03,537 --> 00:13:04,123
Huh?

273
00:13:05,097 --> 00:13:07,647
Don't you worry. We'll deal with this phony.

274
00:13:07,953 --> 00:13:08,667
Uh...

275
00:13:11,621 --> 00:13:12,379
Huh?

276
00:13:23,297 --> 00:13:24,571
What am I doing?

277
00:13:24,987 --> 00:13:27,512
Won't I get in a lot of trouble if I'm busted?

278
00:13:29,258 --> 00:13:32,611
He said we were supposed to meet
our clients on the roof, but...

279
00:13:38,144 --> 00:13:39,737
Um, hello?

280
00:13:40,083 --> 00:13:42,065
I've come from the consultation office.

281
00:13:42,118 --> 00:13:43,956
So, are you three the clients, or uh...?

282
00:13:44,069 --> 00:13:45,992
Huh? Who in the hell are you?

283
00:13:46,017 --> 00:13:48,389
You don't look familiar. Transfer student, right?

284
00:13:48,532 --> 00:13:48,887
Huh?

285
00:13:48,911 --> 00:13:50,190
Consultation office?

286
00:13:50,215 --> 00:13:53,124
You're here to see if you can "get
through" to us thugs, is that it?

287
00:13:53,231 --> 00:13:54,224
So annoying!

288
00:13:54,331 --> 00:13:58,360
Do you really think we're just gonna sit
here and let some twerp like you lecture us?!

289
00:13:58,414 --> 00:13:59,460
No, I'm just...

290
00:13:59,485 --> 00:14:02,081
Why don't you mind your own damn business, do-gooder?!

291
00:14:02,252 --> 00:14:04,649
If you don't, we're gonna make you regret it!

292
00:14:04,729 --> 00:14:06,649
Sorry about that. My bad.

293
00:14:06,956 --> 00:14:09,484
Ugh. Talk about a downer. Let's get outta here.

294
00:14:09,659 --> 00:14:10,370
Hmph!

295
00:14:14,248 --> 00:14:15,797
Hello?

296
00:14:16,272 --> 00:14:18,393
First thing you do is get picked on by thugs.

297
00:14:18,418 --> 00:14:19,118
Way to go.

298
00:14:19,354 --> 00:14:21,386
We're the clients you're here to meet with.

299
00:14:23,046 --> 00:14:24,919
Isn't that Reigen guy coming?

300
00:14:25,412 --> 00:14:27,318
He got caught up at the front gate.

301
00:14:27,405 --> 00:14:29,866
Also, you both came dressed as girls?

302
00:14:29,891 --> 00:14:30,525
Really?

303
00:14:30,598 --> 00:14:33,472
He couldn't get permission to
come in, so we didn't have a choice.

304
00:14:33,646 --> 00:14:34,539
I see.

305
00:14:34,748 --> 00:14:36,653
We're sorry to make you go through all that.

306
00:14:36,678 --> 00:14:40,720
The school just refuses to take us
seriously about any of this supernatural stuff.

307
00:14:40,745 --> 00:14:42,212
So that's why we called you.

308
00:14:42,392 --> 00:14:44,411
What exactly was it that you told them?

309
00:14:44,612 --> 00:14:47,524
Students' belongings are mysteriously vanishing,

310
00:14:47,591 --> 00:14:49,513
and we've been hearing weird noises.

311
00:14:49,538 --> 00:14:51,425
Like, a poltergeist or something.

312
00:14:51,558 --> 00:14:54,680
We heard things have been spotted
floating through the air, too.

313
00:14:54,748 --> 00:14:55,440
Yeah.

314
00:14:55,521 --> 00:14:58,638
Apparently a bra started
floating around in the locker room.

315
00:14:58,765 --> 00:14:59,785
A bra?

316
00:15:00,337 --> 00:15:02,405
We're sure it's not just kids playing pranks.

317
00:15:02,430 --> 00:15:04,052
It's definitely supernatural.

318
00:15:04,077 --> 00:15:05,753
So we went online, looked around,

319
00:15:05,778 --> 00:15:09,726
then called the cheapest exorcist in
the area and somehow ended up with you.

320
00:15:09,886 --> 00:15:11,491
Looks like you get what you pay for.

321
00:15:11,516 --> 00:15:11,850
Huh?

322
00:15:12,471 --> 00:15:16,557
Can't believe a guy was trembling so much
just from dealing with some high school girls.

323
00:15:16,582 --> 00:15:18,887
You must be quite the reliable gentleman.

324
00:15:19,014 --> 00:15:20,156
Oh... Thank you.

325
00:15:20,181 --> 00:15:21,098
That was sarcasm, duh!

326
00:15:21,123 --> 00:15:22,723
She wasn't complimenting you!

327
00:15:22,913 --> 00:15:25,181
Are you sure we can trust him with this?

328
00:15:25,259 --> 00:15:28,705
I have my doubts. You seem pretty unreliable.

329
00:15:29,495 --> 00:15:30,223
What's up?

330
00:15:30,248 --> 00:15:31,139
Something wrong?

331
00:15:31,315 --> 00:15:33,035
I-It's okay...

332
00:15:33,692 --> 00:15:35,765
I just have to perform an exorcism.

333
00:15:38,261 --> 00:15:40,584
Now, let us know if you feel anything spiritual.

334
00:15:41,685 --> 00:15:42,375
Right.

335
00:15:44,831 --> 00:15:46,673
Well? Do you sense anything?

336
00:15:47,123 --> 00:15:48,307
Maybe a little.

337
00:15:48,456 --> 00:15:50,619
Is he being serious right now?

338
00:15:52,105 --> 00:15:53,842
There. It's nearby.

339
00:15:54,570 --> 00:15:55,510
Are you for real?

340
00:15:56,442 --> 00:15:57,535
Someone help!

341
00:15:58,811 --> 00:16:00,312
What's going on?

342
00:16:01,273 --> 00:16:02,873
Something was here...

343
00:16:03,060 --> 00:16:06,130
Something was just looking in from the top of the door...

344
00:16:07,239 --> 00:16:08,778
The windows are locked tight.

345
00:16:09,065 --> 00:16:12,012
And we would've seen if somebody
tried to leave through the exit.

346
00:16:12,306 --> 00:16:14,138
I'm going to follow the spirit.

347
00:16:17,567 --> 00:16:19,723
Whatcha got? Anything so far?

348
00:16:20,581 --> 00:16:22,814
So, we can trust you, right?

349
00:16:23,019 --> 00:16:23,620
Right.

350
00:16:24,639 --> 00:16:26,399
You still can't find it?

351
00:16:27,831 --> 00:16:29,413
The spirit is angry.

352
00:16:29,438 --> 00:16:30,278
Huh?

353
00:16:30,890 --> 00:16:34,056
And, if we keep pursuing it, it might try something.

354
00:16:34,163 --> 00:16:35,996
Wh-What are we gonna do?

355
00:16:36,048 --> 00:16:38,486
The basketball team is practicing inside.

356
00:16:39,056 --> 00:16:40,293
Let's end this.

357
00:16:43,714 --> 00:16:45,072
I've trapped the spirit.

358
00:16:55,425 --> 00:16:56,506
Found you.

359
00:16:59,078 --> 00:16:59,569
Huh?

360
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,873
It's huge!

361
00:17:04,903 --> 00:17:06,917
What is that?! A ghost?!

362
00:17:07,454 --> 00:17:10,316
Now you've done it, you psychic brat.

363
00:17:10,496 --> 00:17:13,837
How dare you trap me in my own haunting grounds!

364
00:17:13,890 --> 00:17:16,963
Are you going to try to ruin my paradise?

365
00:17:17,755 --> 00:17:20,401
If so, then this is what you'll get!

366
00:17:31,538 --> 00:17:34,730
Crap! I underestimated his psychic abilities!

367
00:17:34,850 --> 00:17:37,642
If I don't take a hostage, he'll erase me!

368
00:17:39,789 --> 00:17:42,245
You! You smell nice.

369
00:17:42,434 --> 00:17:44,880
I choose you!

370
00:17:45,054 --> 00:17:46,427
Now, get back!

371
00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:47,645
Huh?

372
00:18:08,905 --> 00:18:10,262
It's all over now.

373
00:18:13,661 --> 00:18:16,189
Listen to them cheer. Good for you, dude.

374
00:18:16,256 --> 00:18:17,134
Thanks a lot.

375
00:18:17,216 --> 00:18:18,902
You were pretty reliable after all.

376
00:18:19,505 --> 00:18:20,950
Damn it...

377
00:18:22,557 --> 00:18:23,336
How?

378
00:18:23,597 --> 00:18:26,557
How was I defeated by a loser like you?

379
00:18:26,831 --> 00:18:29,450
And I thought I'd finally found happiness.

380
00:18:29,997 --> 00:18:32,718
Honestly, you seem to be similar to me.

381
00:18:33,097 --> 00:18:34,131
Similar?

382
00:18:34,777 --> 00:18:37,443
The way you get nervous around girls.

383
00:18:37,790 --> 00:18:41,336
You're playing the loser role in
youth just as I did, aren't you?

384
00:18:42,824 --> 00:18:43,455
I...

385
00:18:44,094 --> 00:18:47,112
I finally started to have fun after I died.

386
00:18:47,623 --> 00:18:48,978
I was content.

387
00:18:49,621 --> 00:18:52,507
But I guess that's all over now. Isn't it...

388
00:18:54,733 --> 00:18:55,625
So...

389
00:18:56,219 --> 00:18:58,851
Are you living every day to the fullest?

390
00:19:11,414 --> 00:19:12,236
What's wrong?

391
00:19:12,261 --> 00:19:14,598
You seem kinda out of it. Somethin' bothering you?

392
00:19:14,842 --> 00:19:16,566
Huh? No, I'm all right.

393
00:19:16,591 --> 00:19:17,337
Thanks, though.

394
00:19:17,939 --> 00:19:19,352
Sure. Okay then.

395
00:19:22,800 --> 00:19:26,223
Ah! Mob! You actually showed up!

396
00:19:26,382 --> 00:19:28,994
We believed in you, Kageyama! We knew you'd be back!

397
00:19:29,187 --> 00:19:32,069
Now, hurry up and sign this club admission form.

398
00:19:33,331 --> 00:19:33,748
Huh?

399
00:19:34,017 --> 00:19:35,248
You're already here?

400
00:19:35,377 --> 00:19:38,653
That was much faster than I expected, Vice President!

401
00:19:38,687 --> 00:19:42,271
Well, I had to make a little
extra time to show this room...

402
00:19:42,491 --> 00:19:43,391
...to them.

403
00:19:44,517 --> 00:19:48,056
This will become the club room of
the newly formed Body Improvement Club.

404
00:19:48,157 --> 00:19:50,432
And they'd like to get set up as soon as possible.

405
00:19:50,578 --> 00:19:52,573
What? Now, just hold on a minute!

406
00:19:52,620 --> 00:19:54,639
The Telepathy Club won't be taken away!

407
00:19:54,713 --> 00:19:57,608
Kageyama was about to sign all
the paperwork needed to join!

408
00:19:57,674 --> 00:19:58,401
Seriously?

409
00:19:58,941 --> 00:20:00,408
Are you out of your mind?

410
00:20:00,594 --> 00:20:01,428
Uh...

411
00:20:01,854 --> 00:20:03,413
Tell me, what grade are you in?

412
00:20:03,438 --> 00:20:04,490
I'm a second year.

413
00:20:04,515 --> 00:20:06,598
Have any experience in other organizations?

414
00:20:06,763 --> 00:20:07,623
No, I don't.

415
00:20:07,648 --> 00:20:10,216
Do you have a close friend or
love interest in the Telepathy Club?

416
00:20:10,241 --> 00:20:11,473
I have an acquaintance.

417
00:20:11,498 --> 00:20:12,397
Cram school?

418
00:20:12,510 --> 00:20:13,496
I don't attend.

419
00:20:13,530 --> 00:20:14,271
Do you study?

420
00:20:14,296 --> 00:20:15,348
Not particularly.

421
00:20:15,373 --> 00:20:16,196
Any hobbies?

422
00:20:16,289 --> 00:20:17,150
I, uh...

423
00:20:17,175 --> 00:20:19,493
Don't you have anything at all you want to do?

424
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:20,453
Huh?

425
00:20:20,997 --> 00:20:24,834
If you let these students goad you into
joining while having no interest at all,

426
00:20:25,047 --> 00:20:27,071
what exactly will you gain from it?

427
00:20:27,264 --> 00:20:28,079
Well, uh...

428
00:20:28,319 --> 00:20:30,871
All I wanna do is live every day to the fullest.

429
00:20:30,896 --> 00:20:33,944
Will wasting time after school
with soda, snacks, and video games

430
00:20:33,969 --> 00:20:36,123
help you "live every day to the fullest"?

431
00:20:36,148 --> 00:20:39,423
If you want to join this club
of your own free will, go ahead.

432
00:20:39,448 --> 00:20:42,311
However, you should carefully think this through.

433
00:20:42,498 --> 00:20:45,203
What is it you really want to do with your life?

434
00:20:45,883 --> 00:20:47,283
What I wanna do...

435
00:20:48,188 --> 00:20:50,166
Do I have anything I wanna do?

436
00:20:50,779 --> 00:20:52,561
Does everyone else have something?

437
00:20:53,141 --> 00:20:56,424
Something enjoyable? Something I'm envious of?

438
00:20:56,651 --> 00:20:57,948
What are they enjoying?

439
00:20:58,674 --> 00:21:00,769
Clubs, hobbies, studying?

440
00:21:01,216 --> 00:21:04,939
Now that I think about it,
hanging out with girls might be fun.

441
00:21:06,607 --> 00:21:08,065
I did have a dream!

442
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:11,178
I wanted to confess my feelings to my first love,

443
00:21:11,203 --> 00:21:14,110
Tsubomi, and hold hands as we walked home.

444
00:21:16,573 --> 00:21:18,153
Take a look, Tsubomi!

445
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:20,848
When you make frogs float, they start swimming.

446
00:21:20,931 --> 00:21:23,423
Oh, wow! That's so cute.

447
00:21:23,490 --> 00:21:25,713
I can make the bar all squishy, too.

448
00:21:26,149 --> 00:21:27,926
You're amazing, Mob!

449
00:21:29,306 --> 00:21:30,048
Look!

450
00:21:30,134 --> 00:21:32,668
I'm only showing you these things, Tsubomi!

451
00:21:33,781 --> 00:21:35,621
I'm getting bored.

452
00:21:37,715 --> 00:21:39,556
The red team can move!

453
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:44,526
You're fast, Akira!

454
00:21:45,662 --> 00:21:46,518
That's it...

455
00:21:46,851 --> 00:21:49,506
If I can change anything by joining a club...

456
00:21:52,164 --> 00:21:53,713
...then I'm gonna join!

457
00:21:54,953 --> 00:21:58,415
Thank you for having me, Body Improvement Club!

458
00:21:59,605 --> 00:22:00,836
Wait, what'd you say?

459
00:22:02,735 --> 00:22:03,122
Huh?

460
00:22:03,676 --> 00:22:05,717
Welcome aboard! Good to have ya!

461
00:22:05,771 --> 00:22:06,717
Thank you!

462
00:23:42,014 --> 00:23:45,748
Unable to locate the whereabouts of
the suspicious individual who infiltrated

463
00:23:45,773 --> 00:23:48,014
an all-girls' school by crossdressing,

464
00:23:48,039 --> 00:23:50,693
the whole area is on high alert...

465
00:23:52,762 --> 00:23:53,705
Hot!

466
00:23:55,418 --> 00:23:57,411
Mob joins the Body Improvement Club.

467
00:23:57,436 --> 00:23:59,181
On his way home, in an attempt to be popular,

468
00:23:59,277 --> 00:24:01,914
he goes to the main temple of
an obviously shady-looking cult.

469
00:24:01,988 --> 00:24:03,164
Are you sure about this, Mob?

470
00:24:03,189 --> 00:24:06,095
Next time, on Mob Psycho 100,
Episode 3: "An Invite to a Meeting

471
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:07,661
Simply Put, I Just Want to be Popular."

472
00:24:07,686 --> 00:24:09,760
Recording it? That's also a wise decision.

